    37→[search]: guide/reading.md#search
    38→[syntax highlighting]: format/theme/syntax-highlighting.md
    39→[theme]: format/theme/index.html
    40→[preprocessors]: format/configuration/preprocessors.md
    41→[backends]: format/configuration/renderers.md
